{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In this futuristic universe, laser hearts and rainbows are your ultimate weapons. Equip your charm-filled arsenal to battle swarms of cutesy robots in procedurally generated cities. With every run, you'll unlock <strong>new weapons</strong>, <strong>skills</strong>, and <strong>skins</strong> to customize your character's look and playstyle!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>KEY FEATURES</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Girly and Fierce</strong> \u2013 Face off against an army of endearing robots while wielding sparkling weapons that shoot hearts, rainbows, and glitter!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Unlock &amp; Upgrade</strong> \u2013 Earn rewards to improve your gear and character, making each new run more powerful than the last.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Co-Op Chaos</strong> \u2013 The fun multiplies in co-op mode! Team up with friends to take down enemies in fabulous cooperative mayhem and unleash glitter storms on your foes!</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>JOIN OUR DISCORD COMMUNITY</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Join the Glitter Gals on <strong>Discord</strong>! Get sneak peeks, exclusive development updates, and who knows\u2014maybe you\u2019ll find your future teammates in the community!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2432230/extras/DiscordBanner.png?t=1738776421\" /></p>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/2432230?t=1738776421","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2432230/page_bg_raw.jpg?t=1738776421","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2432230/cbc5825e2da99891f6790f774c60b4e0b270d3c2/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1738776421","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steams